divs: Sighting Detailsi was outside looking at the moon because it was especially bright. then i noticed a white star like object moving very fast it disappeared for a moment then reappeared just to disapear again....... then another object of the same description followed its path and also disappeared. i have been doing some research on 2012 and planet x and the alignment of earth and the black hole in the center of our galaxy, i don't think it is a coincidence that more people are seeing ufo's as 2012 approaches. There is absolutely no doubt in my mind, This was a ufo. the government is afraid of panic and rioting which is why they have held so much from us for so long.
